name: RTCRtpReceiveParameters
description: The RTCRtpReceiveParameters dictionary, based upon the RTCRtpParameters dictionary, is returned by the the RTCRtpReceiver method getParameters(). It describes the parameters being used by the receiver's RTP connection to the remote peer.
